OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784735286
OL,3,CPolice uncover one of Wiltshire's
OL,4,Clargest-ever cannabis farms
OL,6,FA cannabis farm, thought to be one of
OL,7,Fthe largest ever uncovered in
OL,8,FWiltshire, has been discovered in a
OL,9,Fdisused poultry unit.
OL,11,FPolice found more than 1,500
OL,12,Fcultivated plants, with an estimated
OL,13,Fstreet value of #500,000.
OL,15,FDetectives estimate that roughly #1.5
OL,16,Fmillion worth of electricity was drawn
OL,17,Ffrom the national grid to power the
OL,18,Fillegal enterprise.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
