CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784735286
OL,3,CPolice uncover one of Wiltshire's
OL,4,Clargest-ever cannabis farms
OL,6,FThere have been no arrests at the
OL,7,Fscene, but enquiries are ongoing.
OL,9,FThe recovered cannabis plants are to
OL,10,Fbe taken to a facility where they can
OL,11,Fbe safely destroyed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
